data.description: Discover this enchanting cottage nestled near downtown Cave Springs! Take a leisurely stroll up the charming stone walkway that leads to a spacious frontporch adorned with a delightful swing. Step inside to find a cozy family room featuring a welcoming wood-burning stove, a well-appointed kitchen with anisland, electric range/stove, and ample cabinet space, a separate dining room for intimate gatherings, and a convenient laundry/mud room. The home boaststwo bedrooms, each with faux fireplaces, adding to its charm. Two tankless water heaters. Outside, the backyard awaits as your perfect oasis forentertaining or peaceful relaxation. Two exterior buildings could be a She shed and the other a man cave! Located just a couple of blocks away from CaveSprings' finest restaurants and shops, this home is a rare gem waiting to be discovered. Don't miss out on this exceptional opportunity!
